thread.title: BRIEF-Jiangsu Phoenix Property Investment to swing to net loss in FY 2017

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Jiangsu Phoenix Property Investment to swing to net loss in FY 2017

organizations.name: reuters) - jiangsu phoenix property investment co ltd

text:
Jan 31 (Reuters) - Jiangsu Phoenix Property Investment Co Ltd :
* Sees FY 2017 net loss to be 156 million yuan to 234 million yuan
* Says FY 2016 net profit was 52.4 million yuan
* The main reason for the forecast is effect of national real estate regulatory policy
